swimlanes.description:
This is a generic subassembly which can be used for populating a cloud-log from a Java collection. Access to the collection is provided by an Iterator which provides a sequence of instances which implement CloudLogAdapter. This interface can be used to retrieve the level, message, details and reference ID for each cloud-log entry.
Note that this subassembly intentionally has no local error handler. The error handler should be provided by the subassembly which invokes this utility subassembly as that one is more likely to be able to provide context for which messages are being logged and hence caused the underlying issue
